basics.name: Jing Ting Zheng
basics.label: Student
basics.summary: I am studying for a B.S. in Computer Science at the University of Hawaii at Manoa. I expect to graduate in December 2024.

highlights: Create a full-stack web application using Flask, Python, JavaScript, HTML/CSS, Amazon Web Services to gather diverse research data for machine learning purposes to study affective computing. Running a mixed-methods human-computer interaction (HCI) study to evaluate the usability of the system and the system's capacity to gather useful data and labels for training affective computing AI models.
Organize monthly volunteer projects and events to increase civic engagement in students
Oversee product development and communication for a civic engagement web application to facilitate community service events and engagement among the campus community
Built comprehensive documentation to define downstream and upstream data workflow and integration processes by extracting data using SQL, improving data management and governance
Investigated data transformations in accounting data to translate them into efficient data pipelines and data processing workflows, reducing manual work and increasing operational efficiency
Performed data wrangling and statistical analyses like Pearson correlation coefficient using SAS on multiple large datasets involving over 100,000 participantâ€™s data
mplemented data visualization techniques to communicate findings on the topic of comparing dietary indices in children and adults in the Pacific to the general public
Analyzed Youth Risk Behavior Surveillance System data using statistical analyses in R and communicated results using data visualizations
